				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The way I was thinking it, when you cast the spell, the box would pop up that would allow you to customize your pet. There would be an option, much likke the option we get to save spell lists, for our pets. We could then decide to recast any saved pet we wanted, (ie: raid pet, group pet,solo pet), or create a new one. Thus allowing us a greater area for customizing our pets. 
<br />

<br />
      Also, and the biggest reason, was to further define us as the pet summoners that we are.
<br />

<br />
      I'm betting it would take alot to implement. But, it all has to start somewhere..<img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="razz" border="0" /> 
